ygData.messageBody:
I must say that after 41 levels of EQ, I am a bit bored. It's a
wonderful game, but it doesn't seem to change, except that it
increasingly requires a long session and a good group to get
anywhere.

DAoC looks very good, although I should be disappointed to find that
my EQ friends were on opposing teams and hence incommunicado to me. A
little planning required there.

Anyone tried Anarchy Online? From what I have read, it looks highly
original.

Love, Liz

aka Gyngermynx, ranger of Tunare, 41 seasons and wilting, Quellious
